Name: Aviator: Air Combat
About the game: Don't let the enemy bomber destroy the city. Do whatever it takes to stop it! You are an ordinary farmer who enjoys a peaceful life not far from civilization. One morning you see a plane moving over you, heading towards the town. And all's well and good, but it's military and... enemy... It's time to roll your old single-engine plane out of the barn and remember everything you learned in flight school... All you have to look forward to: 2 maps... 2 bombers Several different types of shells Opportunity to attack the enemy Dozens of difficulty levels And it will all be accompanied by an awesome soundtrack!
